OL,3,CCBI boss to warn Budget tax rises will
OL,4,C'hit growth' among UK firms
OL,6,FTax rises in the autumn Budget are
OL,7,Fundermining investment among UK
OL,8,Fcompanies, according to the head of
OL,9,Fone of Britain's most prominent
OL,10,Fbusiness groups.
OL,12,FRain Newton-Smith, chief executive of
OL,13,Fthe Confederation of British Industry,
OL,14,Fwill warn in a speech on Monday that
OL,15,Fthe measures announced last month have
OL,16,Fmade it harder for businesses to "take
OL,17,Fa chance" on hiring new people.
