OL,6,F"And here's the rub, profitsaren't
OL,7,Fjust extra money for companies to
OL,8,Fstuffin a pillowcase. Profitsare
OL,9,Finvestment... When you hit profits,
OL,10,Fyou hit competitiveness, you hit
