OL,6,FLast week, a closely-watched monthly
OL,7,Fbusiness survey suggested that
OL,8,Factivity across the UK's private
OL,9,Fsector contracted in the first weeks
OL,10,Fof November, amid a drop in firms'
OL,11,Fconfidence after the Budget tax rises.
OL,13,FAnd earlier in November, retailers
OL,14,Fincluding Tesco, Sainsbury's and Marks
OL,15,F& Spencer warned that they will face a
OL,16,F#7 billion jump in their costs because
OL,17,Fof the Budget policy changes, and said
OL,18,Fjob losses were "inevitable".
