OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "Last
OL,7,Fmonth we delivered a once in
OL,8,FParliament budget to wipe the slate
OL,9,Fclean and deliver change by investing
OL,10,Fto repair the NHS and rebuild Britain,
OL,11,Fwhile ensuring working people don't
OL,12,Fface higher taxes in their payslips.
OL,14,F"That meant difficult choices to
OL,15,Frepair the public finances and to put
OL,16,Fpublic finances on a firmer footing.
OL,17,FHowever, the alternatives were more
OL,18,Fausterity, more decline and more
OL,19,Finstability that would have left
OL,20,Fbusinesses and working people worse
OL,21,Foff.
